Antagony listened to the bot and lowered her weapon. She could tell that he 
wasn't hostile, and would indeed take her to a base and a faction.

"Yes," she replied, "that would be nice. Do you know a good faction I can 
join?"

Antagony suddenly yawned and stretched. The ride in the pod had been long 
and very cramped, and her muscles were showing it. She felt a few circuits 
pop back into place and smiled and looked back at Perndabot.
